會者:${receiver!\'\'}拒絕參加該會議，原因:${refuseRemark!\'\'}\n                                <#elseif emailType==\'8\'>\n                                    <#if regularTypeZhTw?? && regularTypeZhTw!=\'\'>\n                                        您成功創建了一個循環會議，將於${meetingTime!\'\'},在${roomName!\'\'}召開。\n                                    <#else>\n                                        <#if roomName?? && roomName==\'\' && recurring==\'10\'>\n                                            您成功創建了一個會議，將於${meetingTime!\'\'}召開。\n                                        <#else>\n                                            您成功創建了一個會議，將於${meetingTime!\'\'},在${roomName!\'\'}召開。\n                                        </#if>\n                                    </#if>\n                                <#elseif emailType==\'9\'>\n                                    <#if regularTypeZhTw?? && regularTypeZhTw!=\'\'>\n                                        您的循環會議\n                                    <#else>\n                                        您的\n                                    </#if>\n                                    [${meetingName!\'\'}]已被修改，請及時關注會議信息。\n                                <#elseif emailType==\'10\'>\n                                    <#if regularTypeZhTw?? && regularTypeZhTw!=\'\'>\n                                        您的循環會議\n                                    <#else>\n                                        您的\n                                    </#if>\n                                    <#if cancelType==\'0\'>\n                                        [${meetingName!\'\'}]已被取消。\n                                    <#elseif cancelType==\'1\'>\n                                        [${meetingName!\'\'}]因為沒有簽到，${roomName!\'\'}已被釋放。\n                                    <#elseif cancelType==\'2\'>\n                                        [${meetingName!\'\'}]因為參會人全部拒絕，${roomName!\'\'}已被釋放。\n                                    <#elseif cancelType==\'3\'>\n    